import axios from'axios';import{tokenHeader}from'../headersauth';import{GET_DATAS,DELETE_DATA,ADD_DATA}from'./types';// GET LEADS
export var getDATAS=function getDATAS(){return function(dispatch,getState){axios.get('/api/project/',tokenHeader(getState)).then(function(res){dispatch({type:GET_DATAS,payload:res.data});}).catch(function(err){return console.log(err);});};};// DELETE LEAD
export var deleteDATA=function deleteDATA(id){return function(dispatch,getState){axios.delete("/api/project/".concat(id,"/"),tokenHeader(getState)).then(function(res){dispatch({type:DELETE_DATA,payload:id});}).catch(function(err){return console.log(err);});};};// ADD LEAD
export var addDATA=function addDATA(lead){return function(dispatch,getState){axios.post('/api/project/',lead,tokenHeader(getState)).then(function(res){dispatch({type:ADD_DATA,payload:res.data});}).catch(function(err){return console.log(err);});};};
